This is a placeholder file.

For a real 3D model, you would:
1. Create an earring model in Blender/Maya/Cinema 4D
2. Export as .glb (glTF binary)
3. Place it in this directory
4. Update the model_url in the jewelry table

To quickly test, download a free earring model from:
- https://sketchfab.com (search "earring gltf")
- https://github.com/KhronosGroup/glTF-Sample-Models
- https://poly.pizza (low poly 3D models)

Then place the .glb file here and update the database.